addToWhitelist(address).details: Add to the list of contracts that can stake in this contract

params._divideBy: list of IPriceProvider to query the and then divide the result
params._divisor: base value used to scale the result by dividing it.
params._governor: The address of the contract which governs this one
params._multiplicator: base value used to scale the result by multiplying it.
params._multiplyBy: list of IPriceProvider to query the price and then multiply the result

removeFromWhitelist(address,uint256).details: Remove from the list of contracts that can stake in this contract

params._hint: Optional hint to start traversing the array, zero is to search all the array.

devdoc.title: This contract gets the price from some IPriceProviders and do the math to calculate a deduced price, for example RIFBTC and BTCUSD gives the price of RIFUSD
